# Frontend Testing and Reporting

## Test Expectations

- Keep existing unit and E2E coverage thresholds intact.
- New UI behavior must be covered by tests in the same change.

## Regression Rule

- If existing behavior changes unintentionally, stop and revise implementation.
- Treat unrelated failures as regressions, not acceptable fallout.

## Intentional UI Change Rule

- When changing UI behavior intentionally, update impacted tests and provide a UI Test Change Report:
  - tests updated and why
  - tests added
  - tests removed (if any) with justification
  - post-change pass/coverage summary
